OL,4,Cas 'very smelly' displayed in hospital
OL,6,FA hospital trust has apologised after
OL,7,Fa sign was displayed describing South
OL,8,FAsian foods as "very smelly".
OL,10,FThe sign, put up in Hospital's
OL,11,Flibrary, explained that hot food was
OL,12,Fbanned and specifically mentioned
OL,13,Fsamosas, pakoras and chapatis.
OL,15,FIt read: "Food and Drink Policy: Hot
OL,16,Fand cold drinks are allowed in the
OL,17,Flibrary.
