OL,3,CSign describing samosas and chapatis
OL,4,Cas 'very smelly' displayed in hospital
OL,6,F"Please do not bring any food into the
OL,7,Flibrary space. Especially not samosas,
OL,8,Fpakoras or filled chapatis as they are
OL,9,Fvery smelly."
OL,11,FA photo of the sign was shared on
OL,12,Fsocial media and has since had
OL,13,Fmillions of views, with many people
OL,14,Foutraged.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for York and
OL,17,FScarborough Teaching Hospitals NHS
OL,18,FTrust said it was "truly sorry for any
OL,19,Fdistress or upset" caused by the sign.
