OL,6,FThey said it was removed "as soon as
OL,7,Fwe were made aware of it" and that it
OL,8,Fis "absolutely not in line with the
OL,9,Fvalues and behaviours of our
OL,10,Forganisation".
OL,12,FThe statement continued: "We are proud
OL,13,Fto have a diverse workforce and are
OL,14,Fcommitted to ensuring the experience
OL,15,Fof all our staff is positive and
OL,16,Finclusive.J"We continue to educate our
OL,17,Fstaff to support them in understanding
OL,18,Fthe implications of actions they may
OL,19,Ftake both positively and negatively."
